Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all\nthe shards of the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:08.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At Mt. Hakurei, Naraku,\nwho has been newly reborn,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}produces another incarnation\nand leaves after slaying Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tragedy brings darkness\ninto our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and yet another trap is set for us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to us and Miroku,\NSango, Shippo and Kirara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Travel back in time\nfor a Feudal Fairy Tale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:24.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:10.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:15.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? So that bastard Naraku\nput up that huge barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and cooped himself up in that mountain\nin order to kill a mere woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Kikyo was no mere woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku feared Kikyo's\nspiritual powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Naraku wanted to rid himself\nof his {\i1}heart....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The human heart\nthat yearned for Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:38.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once before, Naraku tried to cut\nout his human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was when he created Muso,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the one who possessed the heart and\nmemories of the bandit, Onigumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:48.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now feed upon me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:52.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And give me a body\nand power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Naraku absorbed Muso back\ninto his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,saying it had been too soon\nto produce him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This tenacity... This greed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then Naraku {\i1}was....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:42.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those ominous fleshy forms\nwe saw inside Mt. {\i1}Hakurei....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was creating a body\nhe could cast out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which contained his own\nhuman heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:08.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So now that he's killed off\nthat scary priestess,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:12.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,does it mean Naraku can do\njust about anything he wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0} As if I'd let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-We finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm off, Kagome.\NTake care, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, take it easy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:35.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:38.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't hear the mutt complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, where is that idiot anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He looked awfully depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stupid Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:49.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He left Kagome to go\nin search of Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:53.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha hasn't been able\nto accept Kikyo's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand how he must {\i1}feel....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why'd you try to fight him alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't you wait until\NI got there?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if it's flowing into the river,\nthe miasma isn't weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:37.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're there, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:54.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care to know what your\nconnection to that woman was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the one who killed\NKikyo was Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:05.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the one who wasn't able\nto save her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}was you, Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will slay Naraku\nwith my own hands!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you don't have to fight anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will protect you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watching you now,\NI realize it so well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as Onigumo's heart\nexists inside Naraku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}there will be an opportunity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I will use that chance to\ntotally destroy Naraku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and rid him from this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:36.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo didn't believe me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:02.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:03.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo... Did you really die here...\nall alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep up, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're chasing after Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They said a huge demonic\naura went south.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First north, now we're going\nback south.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:31.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we have stayed\nin the south from the start and waited?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:36.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With Inuyasha gone, this is the perfect\nchance to win Kagome over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was pretty nonchalant\nabout leaving her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't understand him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:47.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll find Naraku and destroy him\nin place of Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just wait, Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Day's breaking...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far did you go\nin search of Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha, have you returned?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:27.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You waited up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:32.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Couldn't you find Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to ask, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}thought....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd be able to find\nher remains at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:54.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I say to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't stand to see him\nin such pain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know\nhow to console him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:02.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:03.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm....okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Okay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't look okay at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:28.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This area {\i1}too....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Caused by Mt. Hakurei's collapse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:40.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Shintaro and the others\nare okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:44.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you go.\NEat it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Kagome!\NAll of you together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are all safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? {\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In many villages, demons\nare running rampant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:27.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad that Shintaro\nand the others are all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:32.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Inuyasha looks so troubled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We left Mt. Hakurei so quickly\nin pursuit of Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I wonder if that was\nokay with Inuyasha?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:50.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe he really wanted to stay\nand search for Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a frightening thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could the rumors be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's said Mt. Hakurei crumbled away\nin one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope nothing bad\ncomes from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That demonic {\i1}aura....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:31.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the third {\i1}village....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I only catch the scent\nof weak demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:42.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could this be the work of demons who\nescaped the barrier of Mt. Hakurei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! This is awful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:48.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cornered Naraku and forced\nhim out of hiding...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is even worse\nthan before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of that, Kikyo was killed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, I picked flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Put them over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}there....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:10.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a {\i1}tragedy....{\i0}\NLet me assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Priest....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You came from the area\nof Mt. Hakurei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. I have been on a pilgrimage,\ntraveling around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that Mt. Hakurei,\nthe sacred mountain, had collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and that an evil aura was\nspreading south.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:31.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's exactly as that priestess said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:32.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Priestess?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was about two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An injured priestess had been\nwashed up on the riverbank
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in a region beyond the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She mumbled something about\NNaraku wounding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That she had to go\nafter Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That has to be Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She survived!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo is...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But her injuries were\nso serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She may have died from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:01.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:03.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no time to hesitate.\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo must be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:10.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}O-Okay....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:16.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:31.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to make sure this time,\nif Kikyo is dead or alive...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise, I won't be able\nto go on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha hasn't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, let's go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha will pick up Kagome's scent\nand follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:46.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:57.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there! Halt!\NYou all look suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does he mean your\nappearance, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There have been many\nstrange happenings here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have been ordered to detain\nall suspicious looking travelers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and take them to the castle.\NNow come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:12.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do? We can\neasily beat them and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't start talking like Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, these officials are\nordinary mortals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can escape anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop your mumbling!\NTie them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:35.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to get Inuyasha back.\NLet's go, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:44.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not suspicious! I have the\nproper travel documents!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:44.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Execute him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will we all be killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not even a hearing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is very disquieting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:09.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come, wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is My Lady's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:16.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no use for\nthe others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:30.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:52.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With Kikyo dead, you are the only one\nable to see the Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The priest from {\i1}yesterday....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Honestly, I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Making me baby-sit\na kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}priest....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:16.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:19.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was controlling him with\nmy Dance of the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then the story about Kikyo\nbeing alive was a lie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No one will come to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:29.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The monk and the Demon Slayer will\nbe killed by the clansmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not the woman speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:38.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is obsessed with\nfinding Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:40.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}infant....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is an incarnation of Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:56.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This baby is an incarnation of Naraku,\nborn at Mt. Hakurei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what do you intend to\ndo with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can\nsee the Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Resign yourself to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A hidden weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn wench! How dare she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:57.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm taking these back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These men are nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:53.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still....{\i0} They're just mortals following\norders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:58.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't kill them, on top of that\nwe're far outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This may take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Kagome was taken away\nall alone. We must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:20.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will make good use\nof your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura, untie the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:25.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:19:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think I'll take your eyes\nand eat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? This girl's soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:25.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't find her darkness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That can't be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In every human, there is\ndarkness in the heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anger, hatred, and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:38.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This terrible {\i1}feeling....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like he's digging around\ninside my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Help...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha, help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:01.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm okay now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is searching\nfor Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha won't come to\nsave me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:23.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Found it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've grasped the darkness\nin your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now hold me tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:45.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let our souls unite and\nbecome my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:47.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome was captured while\NI was searching for Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:49.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The human heart is very fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:53.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And hatred is so easily bred.\NThis girl is no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:56.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Use that tainted Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:23:59.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean Kagome will now become\NNaraku's servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:02.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel bitter towards Inuyasha?\NI hate Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:04.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.... But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:08.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Transform Heartache into Courage!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:11.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It means that I love Inuyasha!
